[size=150][b]Description[/b][/size]
This is a simple button that creates a menu with shortcuts (menuitems) to websites. I created this button because I was looking for a way to replace an extension that I used as my homepage ([url=https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/super-start]Super Start[/url]). I called it Speed ​​Dial due to the fact that I've added to it keyboard shortcuts to access the sites.

